Improve exception clarity and add null-safe Painless scripts for nested paths

- GetUpdatedUtcFieldPath exception now explicitly states the model
  doesn't implement IHaveDates and the method must be overridden
- BuildNestedAssignmentScript emits null-initialization preambles for
  intermediate segments (e.g., `if (ctx._source.metaData == null) { ctx._source.metaData = [:]; }`)
  before assigning the leaf field, preventing Painless NPE at runtime
- Simple (non-nested) paths short-circuit with no overhead
